ecify that data is a path or URL to an XML document instead of string data. The default value is &lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;.&#10;@param string $ns (Optional) The XML namespace to return values for.&#10;@param boolean $is_prefix (Optional) (No description provided by PHP.net.)&#10;@return CFSimpleXML Creates a new &lt;CFSimpleXML&gt; element." ilk="function" line="90" lineend="99" name="init" returns="CFSimpleXML" signature="CFSimpleXML init(string $data, integer $options = 0, boolean $data_is_url, string $ns, boolean $is_prefix = false)"><variable citdl="string" ilk="argument" line="90" name="data" /><variable citdl="integer" default="0" ilk="argument" line="90" name="options" /><variable citdl="boolean" ilk="argument" line="90" name="data_is_url" /><variable citdl="string" ilk="argument" line="90" name="ns" /><variable citdl="boolean" default="false" ilk="argument" line="90" name="is_prefix" /></scope><scope attributes="public" doc="Wraps the results of an XPath query in a &lt;CFArray&gt; object.&#10;&#10;@param string $expr (Required) The XPath expression to use to query the XML response.&#10;@return CFArray A &lt;CFArray&gt; object containing the results of the XPath query." ilk="function" line="111" lineend="114" name="query" returns="CFArray" signature="CFArray query(string $expr)"><variable citdl="string" ilk="argument" line="111" name="expr" /></scope><scope attributes="public" doc="Gets the current XML node as a true string.&#10;&#10;@return string The current XML node as a true string." ilk="function" line="145" lineend="148" name="to_string" returns="string" signature="string to_string()" /><scope attributes="public" doc="Gets the current XML node as &lt;CFArray&gt;, a child class of PHP's &lt;php:ArrayObject&gt; class.&#10;&#10;@return CFArray The current XML node as a &lt;CFArray&gt; object." ilk="function" line="155" lineend="158" name="to_array" returns="CFArray" signature="CFArray to_array()" /><scope attributes="public" doc="Gets the current XML 